screen:"Permissions",label:"Terminal Command Auto Execution",description:e==="Cider"?`Google-wide Allowlist: If you are eligible, commands in the this list run without your approval, in addition to the below options. This policy applies to any host, regardless of internet connectivity. Check on eligibility on go/can-i-autorun-agents.

